	h of quirky coworkers. And—worst of all—a different boss. Step inside the 
	chaos of an unpredictable workday as the Unexpected Productions cast impro
	vises an all-new\, on-the-spot mockumentary. From the office know-it-all t
	o the slacker skating by\, you'll meet the characters you love to hate—and
	 hate to admit you recognize. No script\, no second takes—just pure\, unsc
